text: The Netherlands women's national field hockey team is the women's field hockey team that represents the European country of the Netherlands. It is the most successful team in women's field hockey history. == Current squad == As of 7 December 2014 1\. (GK) Joyce Sombroek 2\. Frederique Derkx 3\. Xan de Waard 7\. Willemijn Bos 8\. Marloes Keetels 9\. Carlien Dirkse van den Heuvel 12\. Lidewij Welten 13\. Caia van Maasakker 16\. Michelle van der Pols 17\. Maartje Paumen 18\. Naomi van As 19\. Ellen Hoog 20\. Laura Nunnink 22\. (GK) Larissa Meijer 23\. Margot van Geffen 24\. Eva de Goede 26\. Roos Drost 31\.
